{"tid":2186874,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登8月籌得3.64億美元 打破總統候選人單月籌款紀錄","createTime":"2020-09-03T09:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T15:35:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1d72141b5a93d8fda593c29dd23910022f60d4","tid":2186874,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"最新更新：2020/09/03 17:01<br />\n<br />\n（中央社美國威明頓2日綜合外電報導）美國疫情未歇，造勢活動大受影響，民主黨總統候選人拜登陣營展開一連串線上募款活動，8月募集逾3.64億美元（新台幣108億元），打破總統候選人單月最高籌款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）和紐約時報報導，前一次總統候選人單月最高籌款紀錄，是前總統歐巴馬和民主黨全國委員會在2008年9月創下的2億美元。<br />\n<br />\n現年77歲的拜登在聲明中感謝支持者，直呼「這數字真令我感到震驚」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登還說：「其中有超過2億500萬美元，相當於我們募款金額的57%，都是像你們這樣的線上捐款人，一次捐出5美元、10美元、20美元，一點一滴累積而成。」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n「你們最好相信，他們會竭盡全力攻擊和誹謗我、賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）和我們的陣營。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登8月12日宣布任命加州聯邦參議員賀錦麗為副手後，短短24小時便湧入2600萬美元捐款。<br />\n<br />\n川普和共和黨全國委員會（Republican National Committee）7月募集1.65億美元，而拜登陣營當月僅募集到1.4億美元。（譯者：劉文瑜/核稿：陳政一）1090903<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009030233.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202009030233.aspx&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1d4b1929\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202009030233.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"693de61c3d4603e28e27dd452558403544e66ce8","tid":2186874,"uid":111425,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"查下支那比左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65c9e0d560f7515639907a95ed2626c94a36a71","tid":2186874,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7fdae2d94c878572828a6b1105cd7b5985c43d","tid":2186874,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"人仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdec6c5328cde3a99f9cda966252df703202549e","tid":2186874,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"支共浸到七彩, 都情願拎2億美金去搞鳩美國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9412d6c750451631c6fce4de2c493228de18d21b","tid":2186874,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"我登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6180f25c0508d86d21d3a2de00ef7efab37438d7","tid":2186874,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:35:16.000Z","msg":"贏硬 有金主橕腰 拜登必勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef930cd121de01c20aafe3d4fb692d421eea468","tid":2186874,"uid":53705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bdec6c5328cde3a99f9cda966252df703202549e","tid":2186874,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"支共浸到七彩, 都情願拎2億美金去搞鳩美國先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"你知唔知毛澤東 統治時期<br />\n全中國人無飯食, 餓死八千萬人<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東 都要送糧食比非州 or 其他共產國家 , 拉攏盟友<br />\n<br />\n對於中共來講, 自己民眾餓死, 災難死都無所謂<br />\n最重要係用錢造軍備 + 送比外國拉攏盟友"}]}